<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>CUET Course Details</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="epicacad.css">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('./common/header.ejs') %>
  <div class="container-fluid fs-2 p-4" style="background-color: #E4A11B;">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4"><u>CUET Course Details</u></h1>
    <div class="container bg-white p-4 rounded shadow">
      <div class="row g-4">
        <!-- Course Overview -->
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <img src="images/cuet.jpg" alt="CUET" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h2 class="fw-bold">Course Overview</h2>
          <p>
            The CUET (Common University Entrance Test) course is tailored to help students excel in the national-level entrance exam for admission to central and prestigious universities across India. It includes intensive preparation for the domain-specific sections, general aptitude, and language proficiency.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Duration:</strong> Flexible (6 months to 1 year)</li>
            <li><strong>Mode:</strong> Online/Offline</li>
            <li><strong>Focus Areas:</strong> Core subjects, General Aptitude, and Language</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Key Highlights -->
      <div class="mt-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Key Highlights</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Expert-designed study material aligned with CUET syllabus</li>
          <li>Comprehensive training in reasoning, quantitative aptitude, and verbal ability</li>
          <li>Mock tests and detailed performance analysis</li>
          <li>Experienced faculty and one-on-one mentoring sessions</li>
          <li>Guidance for admission processes and university selection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- Curriculum -->
      <div class="mt-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Curriculum</h2>
        <p>
          The curriculum is structured to cover all CUET sections, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>General Test:</strong> Logical reasoning, numerical aptitude, general awareness</li>
          <li><strong>Domain-Specific Subjects:</strong> Based on student's selected stream</li>
          <li><strong>Language Proficiency:</strong> Grammar, reading comprehension, and vocabulary enhancement</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- Resources -->
      <div class="mt-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Resources and Support</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to live and recorded sessions</li>
          <li>Customized practice papers and previous exam questions</li>
          <li>Interactive Q&A sessions and peer discussion groups</li>
          <li>Personalized feedback to address weak areas</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- Enrollment -->
      <div class="mt-5 text-center">
        <a href="/enrollmentform" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg">Enroll Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('common/footer.ejs')%>
</body>
</html>
